  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t政治话题对赌网站PredictIt今年开了两个关于中共二十大的盘，一个是“习近平是否在二十大连任总书记”，另一个是“胡春华是否在二十大入常”（<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucHJlZGljdGl0Lm9yZy9tYXJrZXRzL2RldGFpbC83MjEwL1dpbGwtSHUtQ2h1bmh1YS1iZS1lbGVjdGVkLXRvLXRoZS1DQ1AtUG9saXRidXJvLVN0YW5kaW5nLUNvbW1pdHRlZS1iZWZvcmUtMjAyMw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.predictit.org/markets/detail/7210/Will-Hu-Chunhua-be-elected-to-the-CCP-Politburo-Standing-Committee-before-2023\">网站链接在此</a>）。这两天听床师的兴致空前高涨，议论得似乎习下李上是板上钉钉了。结果习连任总书记的盘口这两天没怎么大跌，胡入常的盘口暴跌了！<br/>\n小胡：怎么回事呢？！<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjMwMGQ2MTRkMjI0ZjVhY2MzMGViLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b300d614d224f5acc30eb.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b300d614d224f5acc30eb.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b300d614d224f5acc30eb.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGM2OWI3Yjk4Zjg3YzU1MzczZTljLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dc69b7b98f87c55373e9c.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dc69b7b98f87c55373e9c.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dc69b7b98f87c55373e9c.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
